description: Hundreds protest against President Lukashenko, as two main election rivals are barred from running.
title: Belarus election: Hundreds protest after Lukashenko's rivals barred
title_page: Belarus election: Hundreds protest after Lukashenko's rivals barred - BBC News
maintext: The other challenger, former ambassador to the US Mr Tsepkalo, was rejected for failing to gather the 100,000 signatures required to stand in the election, the commission said.
